### Lave CapsLock til Escape, og lad shift + win skifte sprog
exec --no-startup-id setxkbmap -model "pc105" -layout "dkcustom, dk" -variant "nodeadkeys, nodeadkeys" -option "caps:escape, grp:win_space_toggle"

### Disable middle click
exec --no-startup-id xinput set-button-map "ASUE140A:00 04F3:3134 Touchpad" 1 1 3 4 5 6 7

### Picom - transparency, replaces comppton
